### User Module - HTTP Test Requests
### Base URL - Update the port if needed
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Variables
@userId = {{$randomUUID}}
@userEmail = user@example.com
@userPassword = password123

### Test endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/admin/test

### Create User - Cliente
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "{{userEmail}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}",
  "type": "cliente",
  "cpf": "123.456.789-00",
  "phone": "11999999999"
}

### Create User - Prestador
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}",
  "type": "prestador",
  "cpf": "987.654.321-00",
  "phone": "11988888888"
}

### Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### Get User By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}

### Update User
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "phone": "11977777777"
}

### Update User Password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "newpassword123"
}

### Delete User
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}

